    "navbar": "Explore\nProducts\nSupport\nBuy Now",
    "text": "Explore\nProducts\nSupport\nBuy Now\nComing soon.\nUnlock a new way to interact in Procreate 5.3 with Apple Pencil hover on the all-new iPad Pro. Experience a range of new hover features like Brush Size and Opacity gestures, ColorDrop, Gallery Previews and more.\nWATCH PREVIEW\nPROCREATE FOR IPAD\nAn award winning creative experience like no other.\nTODAY AT APPLE\nUnleash your alter ego in this creative project.\nPROCREATE POCKET\nThink bigger.\nPROCREATE INSIGHT\nCatch up with all things Procreate.\nMEET THE ARTIST\nNOVEMBER 21, 2022\nThe intricate mind and brushes of Brad Wooten.\nEVENTS\nNOVEMBER 3, 2022\nCelebrating the world of digital art and animation at LightBox Expo 2022.\nBEGINNERS SERIES\nGet Started\nwith Procreate.\nPROCREATE FOLIO\nShare your art.\nACCESSIBILITY\nArt is for\neveryone.\nWE'RE HIRING\nJoin the\nteam.\nEDUCATION\nUnleash creativity in the classroom.\nDiscover\nWhat's New\nProcreate® for iPad\nProcreate® Pocket\nProcreate® Insight\nProcreate® Art Prize\nLearn with Procreate\nShowcase\nFeatured Artworks\nPopular Artworks\nRecent Artworks\nConnect\nInstagram\nYouTube\nTwitter\nFacebook\nWeibo\nRed\nLine\nDiscussions\nIdeas & Suggestions\nHelp & Support\nMarketplace\nResources\nGeneral\nStories\nArtists' Advice\nHardware & Accessories\nSupport\nFrequently Asked\nPress\nHandbooks\nProcreate Handbook\nProcreate Pocket Handbook\nAccount\nLog in\nCreate an Account\nTerms & Conditions\nPrivacy Policy\nCookies Policy\nCareers\nEnglish (US)\nEnglish (US)\nChinese (Simplified)\nJapanese\nMade in nipaluna (Hobart), Australia.\nCopyright 2022 Savage. All rights reserved. Procreate® is a registered trademark of Savage Interactive Pty Ltd.",
